HEADWORD: Registrar
<hw>Reg"is*trar</hw> <pr>(-tr?r)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[LL.
<ets>registrarius</ets>, or F. <ets>r⟦eacute⟧gistraire</ets>. See
